{"tid":42927,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宋智孝被開除 傳因此斷絕外界聯繫三日躲藏嚎哭","createTime":"2016-12-17T06:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T08:40:24.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf6d63baea2a46ca9a1760b0959c4bdc602d07d","tid":42927,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:02:37.000Z","msg":"《Running Man》爆出「開除」風波後，成員們和節目組16日進行會議，最後決定6人同進退全員下車，節目則在2月底收攤，原先傳出是被迫離開的宋智孝、金鐘國也義氣相挺，確定一起走到最後，不過有相關人士透露，宋智孝其實因此傷透心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，躲起來崩潰大哭。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2216/d2216461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2216%2Fd2216461.jpg&h=06f4f231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宋智孝是《Running Man》的元老成員，日前無預警被「開除」，還是透過媒體才知道自己被迫下車的消息，引爆粉絲怒火，但她卻始終沒有口出惡言，據南韓《OSEN》媒體報導，有相關人士透露，她本人在這3天內備受煎熬、心情沉重，但仍無法放下7年來對粉絲及成員的愛，願意放下傷痛，實現當初許下「要一起走到最後」的承諾。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1581/d1581733.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1581%2Fd1581733.jpg&h=6df7a5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然節目組出面強調，這次風波是溝通缺失所導致的誤會，但破壞了信任和留下創傷已是無法改變的事實，不只《RM》成員因此受到傷害，宋智孝在得知被迫下車的消息時，難過到斷絕和所有人的聯繫，躲起來大哭一場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，也感到相當疲累，讓粉絲跟著心疼落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2208/d2208992.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2208%2Fd2208992.jpg&h=c59998ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為搶救收視率，《Running Man》官方14日無預警汰換固定班底宋智孝、金鍾國，一夕間毀掉成員與官方7年來的情感，宋智孝曾在節目《強心臟》堅決表示：「一起開始了，那就要共同走到最後。」未曾想過退出節目，如今在尷尬的情況下宣布收攤，除了讓粉絲大受打擊，無疑對成員也造成不小傷害。"},{"pid":"f769ec8e4fe57a4cab809c0290d2228f6b54b7c8","tid":42927,"uid":17928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"好呀，褶撚埋佢就岩，條女終於無得再迫我同佢睇呢d弱智節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c2e0431563ddc4ec7df3aa6504e4f1823841a2","tid":42927,"uid":15476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:29:51.000Z","msg":"柒PD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc9a32f2abc77ac5329a04d59dbde3e0a0c31bf","tid":42927,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"點解要炒？班幕後唔係以為個節目會紅係因為佢地嘛&hellip;"},{"pid":"f898f5f7f729ed0e5c6b11cdcc4bc68ac7a4de42","tid":42927,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:25:37.000Z","msg":"Rm好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5928b4d5eb494c1adb027c37fd0f4ea64bdbc2c","tid":42927,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:40:24.000Z","msg":"RM一直好好睇<br />\n直至去完杜拜"}]}